{{Quote|Strangers and friends, we apologize with all our hearts for landing on your dwelling. The tornado picked us up and dropped us here. Not for twelve thousand moons will I ever allow myself to forgive this terrible event.|[[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] to cave dwellers (in N'or)|<ref name="Star Wars Science Adventures: Journey Across Planet X">''[[Star Wars Science Adventures: Journey Across Planet X]]''</ref>}}
'''N'or''' was one of the languages of the [[Delantine system/Legends|Delantine system]], being also the main language on planet [[Da'nor]]. The population of Da'nor used flowery phrases to apologize to one another or to flatter someone.<ref name="Star Wars Science Adventures: Journey Across Planet X" />

